01:14:58,160 --> 01:15:02,654
And there's kind of a sense of
destiny's gonna get worked out

1019
01:15:02,748 --> 01:15:05,115
in this confrontation,
and there's a prelude,

1020
01:15:05,209 --> 01:15:08,952
in which something
