01:15:38,576 --> 01:15:40,988
who've known each other for 15 years,
and they're in a bar

1026
01:15:41,078 --> 01:15:42,949
and Vincent's just saying
this most casual thing,

1027
01:15:43,039 --> 01:15:45,406
"Hey, why aren't you gonna ask
that girl out?"

1028
01:15:58,137 --> 01:16:02,426
With a familiarity that's schizophrenic,

1029
01:16:02,516 --> 01:16:06,054
that has no basis at all
in the circumstances

1030
01:16:06,145 --> 01:16:09,433
that Vincent has, in fact,
imposed upon Max.

1031
01:16:09,523 --> 01:16:12,891
It's a step aside from reality
into a parallel reality,

1032
01:16:12,985 --> 01:16:14,897
the reality that's going on
in Vincent's mind,

1033
01:16:14,987 --> 01:16:17,820
which is also the subtext of the film.

1034
01:16:17,907 --> 01:16:18,692
That Vincent's, in fact, cracking up.

