01:17:41,615 --> 01:17:44,612
shooting in high-def, is the ability
to see these distant landscapes

1057
01:17:44,702 --> 01:17:46,613
and trees against the sky,

1058
01:17:46,704 --> 01:17:49,992
almost as if we're in
some kind of a dark afternoon.

